		<title>Dr. Sharon Briggs, PhD, explains PCOS symptoms and diagnosis</title>
		<link>https://blog.crysta.care/dr-sharon-briggs-phd-explains-pcos-symptoms-and-diagnosis/</link>
				<comments>https://blog.crysta.care/dr-sharon-briggs-phd-explains-pcos-symptoms-and-diagnosis/#respond</comments>
